Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm losing my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... The rumors were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.82,0:00:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.79,0:00:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy snuck in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that’s definitely gonna get him suspended.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t get depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Today again, a boy from our school got suspended.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, our school is not normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,“Co-ed” is just a name—we’ve got completely separated boys’ and girls’ buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So I kind of get why boys try to sneak into the girls’ side just to peek on the maidens...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there {\i1}are{\i0} things girls can’t exactly talk about out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Yuji goes and declares it:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,“I’ll steal a look at you naked.”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Total puttsun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s all about how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.93,0:01:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll prove it within a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:02:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, a beauty appears within the girls’ garden. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori, what are you spacing out about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.89,0:02:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? N-no, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, even if he comes, \Nit won’t be yet. He said a week, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. There’s no way he’d show up \Non the very day he warned us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re too naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t you know infiltration is all about messing with the enemy’s expectations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Disguised as a girl sitting out PE class, snapping photos—no one would ever know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Saori’s still the cutest one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was anticlimactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If he had that much guts, \NI’d want to show him this myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,T-teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect your innocence from suspension.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There—what you boys yearn for the most \Nis this garden of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again on Puttsun Make Love:  {\i1}Infiltrating the Girls' Part of the School!{\i0} and {\i1}Catch it on Film!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, it's so one-sided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone’s gotta wake Yuji up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori, do it once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we stuck with this \Nhorror-movie-maniac freeloader?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I have to wake him up too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t say that. A woman should know \Nhow to make a man rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Golly, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you do {\i1}that{\i0} for Yuji every morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How shameless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna sleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder it vexes me so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The freeloader at our place—that’s Yuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They call him some kind of special-effects genius or whatever, but he’s just gross beyond belief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I even see him in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's totally perverted!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, out of nowhere, Father brings up an arranged marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole thing starts feeling like a nightmare alien movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,An arranged marriage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage meetings are a woman’s training for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re lucky. The candidate is the nephew of Master Hori, ninth-dan of the Kendo Federation,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a respectable young man who'll eventually inherit his family’s trade company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father just called.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That can’t be... \NWhat about my feelings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it’d be this Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But the boy you were supposed to be meeting \Nsuddenly has to fly to New York tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s not my problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But when he saw your photo, \Nhe insisted on meeting you before he leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he’s totally smitten with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Father is simply incorrigible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He sounds like a servant \Ncarrying out his lord’s orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, our Hideki-kun has got a grand future. \NI think he fears nothing in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If he’d just master the Old Master's kendo, \Nthen he’d really be invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s wrong? Are you feeling unwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You should lie down for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re quite the curious one, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.66,0:06:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Following me this far \Nwasn’t just the drugs talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll take you to even nicer parties someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Yuki! Manami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The night of the arranged meeting goes totally puttsun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Puttsun Make Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again on {\i1}Matchmaking Meeting Scramble{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:03.38,Note,,0,0,0,,Product promotion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the master of this fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Swallowing our hatred for hundreds of years, we have wandered this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.04,0:07:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The grudges of our clan—\Nnow is the time to settle them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding! \NSorry for scaring you out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re girls from Jouka Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We came here for a ski camp, and this place happens to be the legendary Yashagatake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe it or not, this lodge was built on the ruins of that fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's where the girls \Nof Jouka Academy are staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Every year, it’s tradition \Nto haze the new teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:08:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, Manami, Yuki, and I were on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Our target was Akimoto-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A worthy opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Inviting Yuji as a special guest was fine and all, but then a real monster appeared right in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Volume 4: Puttsun Make Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:09:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cursed Ski Slope, Jouka's Mountain Villa of Terror. {呪いのゲレンデ 恐怖の城華山荘}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:13.20,Note,,0,0,0,,Product promotion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about yesterday. \NYou came all that way, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, lean on me more. \NIt’s just film—I might even give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen, listen, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Our freeloader—you know, \Nsplatter-obsessed Yuji—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of all people, he was making out \Nwith Akimoto-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it all, clear as day. What a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:10:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fact that I care \Nkind of means I’m weird too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, don’t you think it’s unforgivable for a high schooler to cross that line with a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But then Fukuike-sensei, who secretly has a crush on Akimoto-sensei, witnessed the whole thing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The incident spiraled into an unexpected trip. {????}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami betrays our friendship \Nand invites Yuji to a love hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Akimoto-sensei plays men like toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:11:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And on top of that, my childhood friend Takashi starts coming after my maiden heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything’s blowing up left and right—total puttsun! {acchi mo kocchi mo is the episode title - "there, and here too?!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Volume 3 of Puttsun Make Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There! And Here Too? A Snappy Love Triangle. {あっちも！こっちも？ ぷっつん三角関係}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t care what happens anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:33.55,Note,,0,0,0,,Product promotion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Jouka Academy’s annual big sports festival is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Us girls, under Akimoto-sensei’s guidance,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,train and train for the mass games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One night on the way home from practice, Yuki got molested.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.36,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You never know what might turn out to be a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That incident ended up giving Yuki her first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She was completely lovestruck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But then... It turns out this guy only just transferred to Jouka,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and now he has to transfer again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.52,0:12:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki is devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems, the Norimatsu Gang, some scary friends of that guy are on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami and I, and Yuji too, decided to step in and somehow make Yuki’s first love come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Puttsun Make Love, Volume 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big Sports Festival With Yuki's First Love! {由希の初恋大運動会}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You won’t be able to look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:20.78,Note,,0,0,0,,Product promotion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s summer—it's the beach—a day at the seaside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Manami booking a one-night trip to Izu was great and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but thanks to an unexpected twist, it turned into a one-night trip with just me and Yuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re usually fighting all the time, \Nbut somehow it felt strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fidgety, restless, my heart pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, on that train, we met a mysterious girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:14:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s like there’s a shadow of uneasiness about her—or maybe she {\i1}is{\i0} that shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Her left wrist is wrapped in bandages, and the things she’s carrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A knife, rope, pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, she gives off a dangerous vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But this was my precious \Nmake-love chance with Yuji. {idk how to interpret the show's title anymore}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea at Izu brings an unexpected puttsun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Puttsun Make Love, Volume 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saori and Yuji's Summer Story. {さおりと勇司の夏物語}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I’m doing it for real.
